1
00:00:00,130 --> 00:00:02,080
This is proof the recipe
wasn't plagiarized.

2
00:00:02,250 --> 00:00:03,670
Right?

3
00:00:04,040 --> 00:00:05,040
Yes.

4
00:00:06,580 --> 00:00:08,040
So this is the evidence.

5
00:00:08,580 --> 00:00:09,630
This should settle it then.

6
00:00:16,960 --> 00:00:18,750
I thought this would take much longer.

7
00:00:18,750 --> 00:00:20,170
I even packed
a lunch.

8
00:00:20,580 --> 00:00:22,750
But it was over
much sooner than I thought.

9
00:00:23,330 --> 00:00:24,330
I was hoping...

10
00:00:25,290 --> 00:00:27,750
...your revenge would last longer.

11
00:00:28,170 --> 00:00:29,880
I wanted to spend
more time with you.

12
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:31,710
Stop right there.

13
00:00:35,580 --> 00:00:36,580
Reika-san?

14
00:00:36,790 --> 00:00:38,080
What do you mean by that?

15
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:41,540
You were taking all of that
way too well.

16
00:00:41,540 --> 00:00:42,540
No, that's not it.

17
00:00:43,250 --> 00:00:45,380
You looked like you were enjoying it.

18
00:00:46,080 --> 00:00:47,080
Why?

19
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:49,630
Why would I...

20
00:00:49,630 --> 00:00:50,630
I'm sorry.

21
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:52,460
What are you apologizing for?

22
00:00:53,170 --> 00:00:54,750
Don't give me that look.

23
00:00:55,170 --> 00:00:56,170
Why?

24
00:00:56,790 --> 00:00:58,830
Fight back!
Suffer a little!

25
00:00:58,830 --> 00:01:00,170
I need you to be miserable!

26
00:01:00,170 --> 00:01:01,170
I'm sorry.

27
00:01:01,500 --> 00:01:03,880
Apologizing means you're not suffering!

28
00:01:03,880 --> 00:01:04,880
Why!

29
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:07,250
At this rate...

30
00:01:07,540 --> 00:01:08,420
...I can't get my revenge on you!

31
00:01:08,460 --> 00:01:09,460
I'm in love with you.

32
00:01:17,630 --> 00:01:18,630
Huh?
